{"tid":1536318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係過氣記者佬：你問我答","createTime":"2019-09-03T15:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:04:35.000Z","uid":271365,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d980eea4172a37af799c9919641a05b5ce3aed7f","tid":1536318,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"利申：廢老一名，年老力衰，退下火線好多年。<br />\n<br />\nOK，今晚睇見一班小朋友搭巴士出事<br />\n有部分巴打／絲打對記者直播有啲睇法<br />\n我想以一個過氣報紙佬嘅身分講句：<br />\n各位抗爭者<br />\n你地首要保䕶嘅<br />\n唔係記者嘅採訪自由！（記者有採訪自由，抗爭者都有拒絕採訪嘅自由）<br />\n所以你地無必要俾記者貼身跟住<br />\n<br />\n記者係因為唔知道你地跟住嘅行動<br />\n先會採取貼身跟隨<br />\n只要你地客氣啲同記者講<br />\n「下一步行動未定<br />\n而且＂我地＂呢班抗爭者會分散去唔同地點」<br />\n請記者唔好再跟<br />\n我相信大多數記者會明白<br />\n(當然好難排除個别記者會跟住，咁你地應該盡量撇甩佢地）<br />\n<br />\n如果各位巴絲真係有關於傳媒或記者嘅問題<br />\n我會嘗試講下我所知嘅<br />\n不過，前提係：唔好問我諸如邊個邊個主播或記者正唔正之類涉及個人嘅問題"},{"pid":"9a2174e57df9489dfaea7aebdc19ed5bed0e0c6a","tid":1536318,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"人鏈護警抵唔抵打"},{"pid":"6ed0c80f3bfd1f49a45881b912f55ce4e023854d","tid":1536318,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ace4e73ac0d2e7d32a9be83cbbe6878d8280d382","tid":1536318,"uid":81336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6576e6bced6ff4d92c51e49b0946f0d5b506c2f6","tid":1536318,"uid":306081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f01e5efec4770f846f0cb8affb6ff2f4d89cb287","tid":1536318,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"推 唔通我同條仔扑緊野又要畀你採訪咩"},{"pid":"378aea0c0f3a9de879067033e675a64ff1115ada","tid":1536318,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b287cf1c1bfa40bcb0bbd07dcae8ba6bdce7afda","tid":1536318,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b6b2a26f7ec08cac4e4dbe8a7e7af5301bacb","tid":1536318,"uid":70375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都明好多記者站係邊一邊<br />\n佢地拍低嘅每一分一秒而家同將來都好重要<br />\n但係唔好唔記得一定有狗mon 直播架<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma